summary: Dan is so pretty he has big, doe like brown eyes, fluffy, silky chocolate curls, deep dimples and a cute smile, soft cheeks, a...
body:
Dan is so pretty he has big, doe like brown eyes, fluffy, silky chocolate curls, deep dimples and a cute smile, soft cheeks, a squishy tummy and thighs, little freckles kissed around his face, soft and creamy skin and a boopable nose

Not to mention he has the kindest, cutest and most precious soul. He’s constantly busting into song randomly, he genuinely cares about helping people’s mental health, he’s so smiley and giggly. He’s the best kind of person there is and I love him so much
